Learn SimpleOS step by step
----------------------
1) change folder to "tutorials"

   # lesson00 is for environment setup.
   $ cd ./tutorials/lession00

   # lesson01 is for first exercises for gdb and baremetal program on ARM.
   $ cd tutorials/lesson01/

2) read the README and follow the instructions


Tree of Directory
-----------------
.
├── LICENSE
├── README			# this file
└── tutorials
    ├── lesson00
    │   └── README		# Step by step how-to
    └── lesson01
        ├── gos.lds		# LinkScript for linker
        ├── gos.S		# Main program
        └── README		# Step by step how-to

